CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 18, 1960, pg. 5 reads: "8. Doris Mixon (8), hostess for the Bell Telephone Company of Pennsylvania, demonstrated the beauty and practical use of the new Princess line of phones."
TitMainTitle: Doris Mixon demonstrating Princess phone in Bell Telephone booth in Syria Mosque for the 1960 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama
